    <section class="mainsec amenities-mainsec localarea">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div class="main-heading">
                        <h1>Back Forty Glamping Local Attractions</h1>
                        <p>
                            Explore the exciting activities and attractions that Meaford and the South Georgian Bay area offer. From historic landmarks and cultural sites in and around Meaford to majestic falls and rugged trails in the surrounding areas, our guide spotlights the region’s top experiences.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
