    <section class="addons-sec localarea-silder">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <div id="demos">
                        <div id="localarea-silder" class="owl-carousel owl-theme">
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="addons-item">
                                    <div class="addons-img">
                                        <img src="../../assets/images/meaford-harbour-and-marina.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Meaford Harbour and Marina" loading="lazy">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="addons-desc">
                                        <h3>
                                            Meaford Harbour and Marina
                                        </h3>
                                        <p>
                                            Situated along the shores of Georgian Bay, Meaford Harbour and Marina is not just a docking spot for boats but a gateway to the area's rich maritime and cultural experiences. This picturesque marina is equipped with modern facilities including washrooms, showers, and a lounge area, offering breathtaking views of the bay. Just a short walk from downtown Meaford.
                                        </p>
                                        <a href="https://www.visitgrey.ca/business/meaford-harbour-complex-and-marina" target="_blank" class="btn bookdome" title="Learn More">LEARN MORE</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="item">
                                <div class="addons-item">
                                    <div class="addons-img">
                                        <img src="../../assets/images/blue-mountain-village.webp" class="img-fluid" alt="Blue Mountain Village" loading="lazy">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="addons-desc">
                                        <h3>Blue Mountain Village</h3>
                                        <p>
                                            Blue Mountain Village, nestled at the foot of Ontario's Blue Mountain, offers a unique blend of outdoor adventure and village charm. Visitors can enjoy skiing, snowboarding, and hiking, along with diverse dining, shopping, and entertainment options. The picturesque streets and stunning natural backdrop make it an ideal destination for both adventure seekers and those looking to relax.
                                        </p>
                                        <a href="https://www.bluemountainvillage.ca/" target="_blank" class="btn bookdome" title="Learn More">LEARN MORE</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
